<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/pff/puhca/part2.html 204.71.237.88 19970209120957 text/html 6460
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 12:10:44 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:55 GMT
