HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 12:05:12 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:46 GMT
Content-length: 7191
Content-type: text/html
