<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/sbsc/sen-1296.html 204.71.237.88 19970208171835 text/html 2746
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 17:19:18 GMT
