http://www.conservative.org:80/sbsc/sept96/cwcpr.html 204.71.237.88 19970208174809 text/html 4446
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 17:48:56 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:52 GMT
Content-length: 4261
Content-type: text/html
