<html>
<head>
<title>Michelle Sharp</title>
</head>

<body>

<h2>Michelle Sharp</h2>

<img alt="Picture of Michelle Sharp" src="sharp2.gif"><p>

	Michelle Sharp is a program officer of Young America's Foundation, responsible for the speakers program.  She has organized hundreds of college lectures and has furthered the program as the best in the country.  Under her guidance, Young America's Foundation has reached a new communications level with internet access through Town Halll.<p>

	Miss Sharp graduated from Liberty University with a B.S. in Social Sciences.  She worked for the Oliver North for Senate Committee on the finance committee.<p><p>

