HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 03:52:10 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:28 GMT
Content-length: 6192
Content-type: text/html
